---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="Telos — 332 Projects"
	description="Telos is a multifunction Discord bot with an AI assistant and smart memory system, built for 332."
>
	<div class="page-root relative min-h-screen px-4 pb-32 pt-32">
		<div class="dot-pattern pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>

		<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
			<div
				class="absolute -left-[10%] top-[5%] h-[600px] w-[600px] rounded-full"
				style="background: radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.9 0 0 / 6%), transparent 65%); filter: blur(100px);"
			></div>
			<div
				class="absolute -right-[5%] top-[40%] h-[500px] w-[500px] rounded-full"
				style="background: radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.8 0 0 / 5%), transparent 65%); filter: blur(80px);"
			></div>
		</div>

		<div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl">

			<!-- Breadcrumb -->
			<nav class="mb-10" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
				<a
					href="/projects"
					class="glass-nav-link inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5 text-sm tracking-wider text-muted-foreground transition-all hover:text-foreground no-underline"
				>
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
						<path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/>
					</svg>
					All Projects
				</a>
			</nav>

			<!-- Hero -->
			<div class="mb-12 animate-[fade-in-up_0.7s_ease-out_both]">
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
					<div class="mb-6 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
						<div>
							<p class="section-label">Project</p>
							<h1 class="text-4xl tracking-wider text-foreground sm:text-5xl">
								Telos<span class="blink-cursor">_</span>
							</h1>
						</div>
						<span
							class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-wider"
							style="background: oklch(0.65 0.15 145 / 10%); border: 1px solid oklch(0.65 0.15 145 / 30%); color: oklch(0.65 0.15 145);"
						>
							<span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: oklch(0.65 0.15 145); box-shadow: 0 0 4px oklch(0.65 0.15 145 / 60%);"></span>
							Live
						</span>
					</div>
					<p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg">
						[A compelling 1-2 sentence description of Telos. What makes it different from other bots? The AI memory system angle is interesting — lead with that.]
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Overview -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
					<p class="section-label">Overview</p>
					<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl tracking-wider text-foreground">What it does<span class="blink-cursor">_</span></h2>
					<div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-base">
						<p>
							[Describe Telos in more detail. What's the scope — moderation? utilities? AI conversation? CTF integration? Give a clear picture of the full feature set and purpose.]
						</p>
						<p>
							[What problem was Telos built to solve? What gap did it fill vs. existing bots? Why was it worth building instead of using something off-the-shelf?]
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- AI Memory System -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
					<p class="section-label">Key Feature</p>
					<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl tracking-wider text-foreground">AI Memory System<span class="blink-cursor">_</span></h2>
					<div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-base">
						<p>
							[Describe the AI memory system. How does it work? What makes it "smart"? Is it per-user memory, per-channel context, global state? How does the AI assistant use this memory in practice?]
						</p>
						<p>
							[Technical implementation if you want to share it — what models, what storage, what retrieval approach. Or keep it high level if you prefer.]
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Features grid -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<p class="section-label mb-6">Feature Set</p>
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
					{[
						{ title: 'AI Assistant', desc: '[What the AI can do — conversations, commands, context-awareness, memory recall. What makes it useful day to day.]' },
						{ title: 'CTF Integration', desc: '[How Telos integrates with the CTF platform — commands to access challenges, check scores, start instances, etc.]' },
						{ title: 'Moderation', desc: '[What moderation features Telos handles — warnings, bans, automod, logging, role management, etc.]' },
						{ title: '[Feature Name]', desc: '[Description of another feature]' },
						{ title: '[Feature Name]', desc: '[Description of another feature]' },
						{ title: '[Feature Name]', desc: '[Description of another feature]' },
					].map(f => (
						<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-5">
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-sm tracking-wider text-foreground">{f.title}</h3>
							<p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">{f.desc}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Commands reference -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
					<p class="section-label">Reference</p>
					<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl tracking-wider text-foreground">Commands<span class="blink-cursor">_</span></h2>

					<p class="mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
						[Short intro — slash commands? prefix? how do you access Telos in the server?]
					</p>

					<div class="space-y-2">
						{[
							['/[command]', '[What it does]'],
							['/[command]', '[What it does]'],
							['/[command]', '[What it does]'],
							['/[command]', '[What it does]'],
							['/[command]', '[What it does]'],
						].map(([cmd, desc]) => (
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2 last:border-0 last:pb-0">
								<code class="shrink-0 rounded bg-white/5 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs tracking-wider text-foreground">{cmd}</code>
								<span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">{desc}</span>
							</div>
						))}
					</div>

					<p class="mt-6 text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-foreground">
						[Note about full command list — e.g. "Full command list available to members in the server" or link to docs]
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Tech stack -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
					<p class="section-label">Technical</p>
					<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl tracking-wider text-foreground">Stack<span class="blink-cursor">_</span></h2>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						{['[Language]', '[Framework/Library]', '[AI Model/API]', '[Database]', '[Hosting]'].map(t => (
							<span class="glass-button rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-foreground">{t}</span>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Screenshots placeholder -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<p class="section-label mb-6">Screenshots</p>
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
					{[1, 2].map(n => (
						<div
							class="glass-card flex h-48 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl"
							style="border-style: dashed;"
						>
							<p class="text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">[Screenshot {n}]</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Related projects -->
			<section>
				<p class="section-label mb-4">Related</p>
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<a href="/projects/ctf" class="glass-card group block rounded-2xl p-5 no-underline transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
						<h3 class="mb-1 text-sm tracking-wider text-foreground">CTF Platform</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Accessible through Telos</p>
					</a>
					<a href="/projects/332-labs" class="glass-card group block rounded-2xl p-5 no-underline transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
						<h3 class="mb-1 text-sm tracking-wider text-foreground">332 Labs</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Telos will integrate with Labs</p>
					</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer class="border-t border-white/5 px-4 py-8">
		<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 sm:flex-row">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
				<img src="/polygon.svg" alt="332" class="h-5 w-5 opacity-60" width="20" height="20" />
				<span class="text-sm tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">332</span>
			</div>
			<div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-foreground">
				<a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors no-underline">Home</a>
				<a href="/projects" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors no-underline">Projects</a>
				<a href="/blog" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors no-underline">Blog</a>
			</div>
			<p class="text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-foreground opacity-40">
				© {new Date().getFullYear()} 332
			</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</PageLayout>
